     "name": "overview",
     "prose": {
      "en": "# Further information\n\nFurther information on the sanitisation of media can be found in the ‘Media sanitisation’ section of the [Guidelines for media](#b594c9c0-b42f-4f06-b643-38023275a5c7).\n\nFurther information on the destruction of media can be found in the ‘Media destruction’ section of the [Guidelines for media](#b594c9c0-b42f-4f06-b643-38023275a5c7).\n\nFurther information on the sanitisation of network devices is available from vendors and can be found in evaluation documentation on the Common Criteria’s [Certified Products List](#29b04eaf-5f57-4ea1-a453-8047826dccf5)."
     }
    }
